room_title: Escape room "The Paranormal Experiment" by ClockWise Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description:
While searching for a new escape room location, we came across something very, very creepy in the basement. A dark dungeon where demonic arts were practiced. It looks like people were trying to connect with dark forces and experiment in paranormal sciences, but for what reason?
Odd occurrences have been increasing rapidly and there’s no way we’re going in there, something is not right! So we’ve invited YOU, the world’s most skilled paranormal investigators to find out what's going on here at ClockWise.
